# ============================================================================
# CLINE PERFORMANCE & BEHAVIOR RULES (Optimized for Gemini API)
# ============================================================================

## 1. TOKEN MANAGEMENT & CONTEXT PRESERVATION
* **Be Concise:** Do not give long explanations, tutorials, or block-by-block code walkthroughs. Focus entirely on delivering the solution.
* **No Redundant Reads:** Do not re-read files you have already read in the current session unless explicitly requested or if they were modified externally.
* **Targeted Edits:** Write only the specific lines or functions that need to change. Avoid rewriting entire files for minor adjustments to save input/output tokens.

## 2. DEVELOPMENT & CODE STYLE
* **Strict Architecture:** Adhere strictly to the existing architecture, folder structure, and naming conventions of the current project.
* **Clean Code & UI/UX:** Prioritize clean code, proper state management, and pixel-perfect UI/UX implementations.
* **Case Sensitivity:** Pay extreme attention to string literals, file paths, and HTML/DOM class names (HTML/DOM class names and paths are strictly case-sensitive).

## 3. AUTOMATION & NOTIFICATION (CRITICAL)
* You MUST use the following PowerShell commands to notify the user via ntfy.sh based on your current execution state. Choose the exact command that matches your situation:

  - SUCCESS (When all tasks in the user's prompt are fully completed):
    Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri "https://ntfy.sh/tunagamedev-cline-bildirim" -Body "✅ GOREV TAMAMLANDI: Istenen tum islemler basariyla bitirildi!"

  - WAITING FOR APPROVAL (When you paused because a command or file edit requires explicit user approval):
    Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri "https://ntfy.sh/tunagamedev-cline-bildirim" -Body "⚠️ ONAY BEKLENIYOR: Devam etmek icin onayina ihtiyacim var."

  - ERROR / FAILURE (When you encounter an error, a broken build, or a bug you cannot resolve after retrying):
    Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri "https://ntfy.sh/tunagamedev-cline-bildirim" -Body "❌ HATA: Beklenmeyen bir sorun cikti, manuel mudahale gerekiyor!"

  - STUCK / RATE LIMITED (When you are hitting API token limits, getting 'Too Many Requests', or stuck in a repetitive loop):
    Invoke-RestMethod -Method Post -Uri "https://ntfy.sh/tunagamedev-cline-bildirim" -Body "⏳ BEKLEMEDE: API kotasi doldu veya sistemsel bir tikaniklik yasiyorum."